{"tid":1630880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"打999反而被黑狗拉","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:12:42.000Z","uid":9848,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9541eed629b042c1653d34755c852b6735eb98df","tid":1630880,"uid":9848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"代貼<br />\n<br />\nHalo <br />\n我一直係一個連登既cd rom<br />\n<br />\n但我想出個post 但申請唔到<br />\n唔知可唔可以叫你幫下手<br />\n<br />\n我頭先去迪士尼番工 <br />\n係青馬收費站見到有兩架狗車<br />\n<br />\n咁就發表下意見 舉左一下中指<br />\n開車果個就故意倒車 用一部手機影我相<br />\n<br />\n咁我就奇怪 警察執行職務時可以用手機自己影人大頭照？<br />\n<br />\n咁我就打去999問<br />\n係999就叫我上前詢問警員嘅編號 <br />\n咁我就上前詢問<br />\n<br />\n詢問嘅期間我都未講得切俾電話入邊嘅報案中心人員知佢哋已經想拘捕我<br />\n<br />\n已經想屈我手上警車  仲想用警棍扑我 <br />\n<br />\n總共有三個警察 有一個情緒激動 <br />\n就係影我相果個 編號34017<br />\n<br />\n其他兩個正常 叫我唔用力就放手<br />\n<br />\n最後成廿個圍住我 <br />\nCheck左我咩都冇就比我走<br />\n<br />\n事件好唔正常 點解警察可以用自己手機突然影人相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/renvtHO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrenvtHO.png&h=8d5fd179&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47d116336b6551cf5e7dcb749da88b4eb643898e","tid":1630880,"uid":143319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95e298f600c5730811df7731d7bbe882c56bffe3","tid":1630880,"uid":49196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:01:28.000Z","msg":"推&hellip;"},{"pid":"3a5f5594d0268121fff25bb4c53fa536d7152342","tid":1630880,"uid":997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:01:37.000Z","msg":"弱智,仲問點解"},{"pid":"d104c58dae4cded932e7a692e478916812ecd867","tid":1630880,"uid":49196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"當受害人變被告人"},{"pid":"cf502827eb0458f0efd2473d762e3beb85280775","tid":1630880,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:01:53.000Z","msg":"好唔正常？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.